example.code:
Get-CFCloudFrontOriginAccessIdentityList -MaxItem 2
IsTruncated : True Items : {E326XXXXXXXXXT, E1YWXXXXXXX9B} Marker : MaxItems : 2 NextMarker : E1YXXXXXXXXX9B Quantity : 2
example.description: This example returns a list of Amazon CloudFront origin access identities. Because the -MaxItem parameter specifies a value of 2, the results include two identities.
